backgroundInformationList.description: Notice of Passing of By-law 636-2021 - 425 Cherry Street

noticeDescription: Take notice that the Council of the City of Toronto has passed By-law 636-2021 to designate the property at 425 Cherry Street (Ward 13 Toronto Centre) as being of cultural heritage value or interest.
